{"lang": "zh_TW", "eventid": "act31side", "eventName": "懷黍離", "entryType": "ACTIVITY", "storyCode": "HS-ST-3", "avgTag": "幕間", "storyName": "徹風雨", "storyInfo": "望、績二人的謀劃令朝野震動，針對歲獸的戰爭已經無可避免。\n在被人遺忘後，黍孤身一人去往了別的地方，她要做的事，依舊沒有改變。\n", "storyList": [{"id": 0, "prop": "HEADER", "attributes": {"key": "title_test", "is_skippable": "true", "fit_mode": "BLACK_MASK"}}, {"id": 1, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 2, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 3, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 4, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 5, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "25_g06_mountainroad_d", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 6, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 7, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"key": "$midautumn", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 8, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 9, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "咳咳咳……", "name": "？？？"}}, {"id": 10, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "咳咳……咳……呼……", "name": "？？？"}}, {"id": 11, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 12, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 13, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_walk_n", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 14, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "left", "name": "avg_npc_1239_1#1$1", "duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 15, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 16, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "left", "name": "avg_npc_1239_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 17, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你就非要約我來爬這天岳。", "name": "癆病的老人"}}, {"id": 18, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這個陽處的位置我先佔了，你坐那邊去。我身子沒你好，你別跟我搶。", "name": "癆病的老人"}}, {"id": 19, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 20, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_walk_n", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 21, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "right", "name": "avg_npc_301_1#5$1", "duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 22, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 23, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "right", "name": "avg_npc_301_1#5$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 24, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "出來散散步，曬曬太陽，嚐嚐這天岳的泉水，對你的身體有好處。", "name": "太傅"}}, {"id": 25, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "left", "name": "avg_npc_1239_1#3$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 26, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "真好笑，我們幾十年沒在那堵宮牆外打過照面，這次是你主動約的。", "name": "太尉"}}, {"id": 27, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……到底還是你先坐不住了。", "name": "太尉"}}, {"id": 28, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "right", "name": "avg_npc_301_1#2$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 29, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "很難坐得住。", "name": "太傅"}}, {"id": 30, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "玉門，大荒城。這一連串的事，總要一個說法。", "name": "太傅"}}, {"id": 31, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "left", "name": "avg_npc_1239_1#9$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 32, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "對，都是我幹的。", "name": "太尉"}}, {"id": 33, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "玉門山海眾是我教唆的，睚也是我引入關的。", "name": "太尉"}}, {"id": 34, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "right", "name": "avg_npc_301_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 35, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "太傅"}}, {"id": 36, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "left", "name": "avg_npc_1239_1#9$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 37, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這些夠把我拉下台嗎？要是嫌不夠，望是我放出京城的，那個孩子是我送去維多利亞的，邪魔的口子也是我撕開的。", "name": "太尉"}}, {"id": 38, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "只要有需要，讓三公的位置再空一個出來，這些事都可以是我做的。", "name": "太尉"}}, {"id": 39, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "right", "name": "avg_npc_301_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 40, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "太傅"}}, {"id": 41, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "left", "name": "avg_npc_1239_1#4$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 42, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "山海眾，烏合之眾，能成什麼氣候？", "name": "太尉"}}, {"id": 43, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "睚，不過是條癆病獸，派上幾十上百個天師，總能打發了，不過用來當作喚醒歲的口糧倒是正好。", "name": "太尉"}}, {"id": 44, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "老魔小丑，不足掛齒。", "name": "太尉"}}, {"id": 45, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "left", "name": "avg_npc_1239_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 46, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "咳……咳……呼……說到底，我也不過是個老癆病鬼，我這條命，也就只剩這點用得到的地方。", "name": "太尉"}}, {"id": 47, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "right", "name": "avg_npc_301_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 48, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你就不怕事情超出掌控，你從來不會怕。", "name": "太傅"}}, {"id": 49, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "left", "name": "avg_npc_1239_1#2$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 50, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我怕的東西可太多了……我怕“人心叵測”，我怕“大勢所趨”。", "name": "太尉"}}, {"id": 51, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "見風使舵，一人拉一邊，是求個平衡。", "name": "太尉"}}, {"id": 52, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "left", "name": "avg_npc_1239_1#3$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 53, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "可事到如今，那個罪人已經掀了棋盤，我們還有半分求和的可能嗎？", "name": "太尉"}}, {"id": 54, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "玉門城已經修復完畢，在趕來京城的路上了。太傅大人，早做打算吧。", "name": "太尉"}}, {"id": 55, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 56, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 57, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 58, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "47_g6_civilengineermasteroffice", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 59, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 60, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 61, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "left", "name": "avg_4121_zuole_1#1$1", "duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 62, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "right", "name": "avg_npc_039_1", "duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 63, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 64, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "left", "name": "avg_4121_zuole_1#6$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 65, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "復職信……？", "name": "左樂"}}, {"id": 66, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "right", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 67, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這封信原本不該由我來送。", "name": "麟青硯"}}, {"id": 68, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "大荒城的事件，那兩個罪人的所作所為，朝廷已經得知。", "name": "麟青硯"}}, {"id": 69, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "現在司歲台、天師府、六部……朝野上下，全都忙成一團。我出公事經過大荒城，就代勞了。", "name": "麟青硯"}}, {"id": 70, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "left", "name": "avg_4121_zuole_1#10$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 71, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "是母親她，拜託你來的吧……", "name": "左樂"}}, {"id": 72, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "right", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 73, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "麟青硯"}}, {"id": 74, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "left", "name": "avg_4121_zuole_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 75, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……多謝。", "name": "左樂"}}, {"id": 76, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這次代理人引發的動亂，朝中已經有結論了？", "name": "左樂"}}, {"id": 77, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "right", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 78, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "是。", "name": "麟青硯"}}, {"id": 79, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "玉門城已修復完畢，已重新啟動駛向京城。", "name": "麟青硯"}}, {"id": 80, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "left", "name": "avg_4121_zuole_1#3$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 81, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "左樂"}}, {"id": 82, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "還是到了這一步。", "name": "左樂"}}, {"id": 83, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "right", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 84, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你倒是鎮定，我還以為你會立刻吵著要回到前線呢。", "name": "麟青硯"}}, {"id": 85, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "left", "name": "avg_4121_zuole_1#4$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 86, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這段時間，我想明白一個道理。", "name": "左樂"}}, {"id": 87, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "恐懼才會急躁……越是不敢面對未知的敵人，就越想埋頭衝過去，不管結果如何，只當給自己一個交代。", "name": "左樂"}}, {"id": 88, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……可我現在不會害怕了。", "name": "左樂"}}, {"id": 89, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那些代理人，縱使有改天換地的能力，可說到底，他們也有人情人性，在這方面，祂們與我們並無不同。", "name": "左樂"}}, {"id": 90, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "“對手”並非不可捉摸，那就沒什麼好怕的。", "name": "左樂"}}, {"id": 91, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 92, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 93, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 94, "prop": "CameraEffect", "attributes": {"effect": "Grayscale", "fadetime": 0.0, "keep": "true", "initamount": 0.0, "amount": 0.7, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 95, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "bg_landscape", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 96, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1236_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 97, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 98, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "左公子，在下的確無意與你為敵。剛才說過的話，只希望左公子記得。", "name": "績"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1236_1#1$1"}, {"id": 99, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "來日方長，我們還會有再見面的時候。", "name": "績"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1236_1#1$1"}, {"id": 100, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 101, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 102, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 103, "prop": "CameraEffect", "attributes": {"effect": "Grayscale", "fadetime": 0.0, "amount": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 104, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "left", "name": "avg_4121_zuole_1#4$1"}}, {"id": 105, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "right", "name": "avg_npc_039_1"}}, {"id": 106, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "47_g6_civilengineermasteroffice", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 107, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 108, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "right", "name": "avg_npc_039_1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 109, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "還不錯，左將軍讓你來這裡修心，也不算白來了。", "name": "麟青硯"}}, {"id": 110, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "left", "name": "avg_4121_zuole_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 111, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我已經準備妥當，隨時可以動身。現在該去哪？玉門，還是百灶？", "name": "左樂"}}, {"id": 112, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "right", "name": "avg_npc_039_1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 113, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不急，先回歸一下你的本職工作吧。", "name": "麟青硯"}}, {"id": 114, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "有一個地方，與代理人接觸頗多。雖說朝廷對那裡並非一無所知，依照慣例，還是由司歲台去調查一下為好。", "name": "麟青硯"}}, {"id": 115, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "left", "name": "avg_4121_zuole_1#10$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 116, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……羅德島？", "name": "左樂"}}, {"id": 117, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 118, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 119, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 120, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 121, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "47_g3_fieldpath", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 122, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 123, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$warm_intro", "key": "$warm_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 124, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 125, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "left", "name": "avg_4119_wanqin_1#2$1", "duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 126, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "right", "name": "avg_4122_grabds_1#2$1", "duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 127, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 128, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "right", "name": "avg_4122_grabds_1#8$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 129, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你真的要走了？", "name": "小滿"}}, {"id": 130, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "left", "name": "avg_4119_wanqin_1#10$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 131, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "真的。", "name": "禾生"}}, {"id": 132, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這一批種子，有些種了出來，源石耐受性的表現比預想的要好，是時候帶去外面的田地裡做下一步培育了。", "name": "禾生"}}, {"id": 133, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "right", "name": "avg_4122_grabds_1#7$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 134, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那是不是很辛苦？", "name": "小滿"}}, {"id": 135, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "left", "name": "avg_4119_wanqin_1#10$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 136, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "和在大荒城做的事一樣。", "name": "禾生"}}, {"id": 137, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "right", "name": "avg_4122_grabds_1#11$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 138, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "唔……那你什麼時候回來？", "name": "小滿"}}, {"id": 139, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "left", "name": "avg_4119_wanqin_1#10$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 140, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "先是把種子送去全國各個糧食種植基地，培育第一批試種植株，再根據莊稼對不同土地的適應狀況，找合適的培育方法。", "name": "禾生"}}, {"id": 141, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "left", "name": "avg_4119_wanqin_1#4$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 142, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "要得出確切的結果，可能要十代以上的培育。應該是，很長一段時間……", "name": "禾生"}}, {"id": 143, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "right", "name": "avg_4122_grabds_1#4$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 144, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "嗯……一代莊稼就是一年，十年……那是多長一段時間呢？", "name": "小滿"}}, {"id": 145, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "right", "name": "avg_4122_grabds_1#9$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 146, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "夠綿綿長得和他的爸爸媽媽一樣大……好像也不是很長嘛，換了新飼料後，牧獸都長得很快，每天都會變大一圈。", "name": "小滿"}}, {"id": 147, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "right", "name": "avg_4122_grabds_1#8$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 148, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "可是十年，也是要等忘花果樹結十回酸果子……這麼一想，又好像永遠都等不到似的。", "name": "小滿"}}, {"id": 149, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "left", "name": "avg_4119_wanqin_1#9$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 150, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "禾生"}}, {"id": 151, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "right", "name": "avg_4122_grabds_1#8$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 152, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "唉，我再送送你吧。", "name": "小滿"}}, {"id": 153, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 154, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_walk_n", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 155, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 156, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 157, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_relaxflutem", "volume": 0.7}}, {"id": 158, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 159, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "笛聲纏綿著，伴著夕陽跟在二人身後。泥土路上，兩排腳印踏出去很遠。"}}, {"id": 160, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 161, "prop": "Stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 3.0}}, {"id": 162, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 3.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 163, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 164, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 165, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "bg_town", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 166, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_hgsldpn", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 167, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 168, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$newhope01_intro", "key": "$newhope01_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 169, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 170, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "江南。"}}, {"id": 171, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "大哥曾經說過，卸任之後，想去江南看看。"}}, {"id": 172, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "幾百年沒有嚐過江南夏天的菱角，見慣了黃沙戈壁，就在小橋流水的小鎮裡歇歇吧。只是要小心點，別再把這幅畫打破了。"}}, {"id": 173, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 174, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 175, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 176, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "35_g3_yumenobservationtower_d", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 177, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 178, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 179, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "令始終忘不了那片大漠。"}}, {"id": 180, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "她不是喜歡戰爭，只是喜歡沙場上人們的豪情萬丈罷了……誰會不喜歡？"}}, {"id": 181, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "畫裡沒有吹角連營的戰火，只有大漠孤煙，長河落日。你就安心在這裡喝你的酒，當你的詩人吧。"}}, {"id": 182, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 183, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 184, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 185, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "25_g03_yandowntown_n", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 186, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 187, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 188, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "年會喜歡熱鬧的地方，但比起龍門，還是尚蜀的口味更適合她。"}}, {"id": 189, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你就老老實實在這裡待著，別來煩我了。"}}, {"id": 190, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 191, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 192, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 193, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "bg_indoor", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 194, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 195, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 196, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "二哥……應該只給他畫一副棋盤的。"}}, {"id": 197, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "心思都在算計上，審美也太差了點……這個園子送你，我也不想再見你了。"}}, {"id": 198, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "算到最後，竟也沒有給自己留半分退路，你到底……呵。"}}, {"id": 199, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 200, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 201, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 202, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "25_g08_pavilion", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 203, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 204, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 205, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "頡……"}}, {"id": 206, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "要不是你太愛嘮叨，又總擺一副姐姐的架子，我真的想過要找你學書法的。"}}, {"id": 207, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 208, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 209, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 210, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avgnew_2015_dusk_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 211, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "47_g10_fairyfarmland_ex", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 212, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 213, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 214, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……行了，就這樣吧。", "name": "夕"}, "figure_art": "avgnew_2015_dusk_1#1$1"}, {"id": 215, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avgnew_2015_dusk_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 216, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "費了這些心思，誰知道大夢醒時，這些畫還能不能留住。", "name": "夕"}, "figure_art": "avgnew_2015_dusk_1#2$1"}, {"id": 217, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avgnew_2015_dusk_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 218, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "留得下如何，留不下又如何。", "name": "夕"}, "figure_art": "avgnew_2015_dusk_1#1$1"}, {"id": 219, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "來過了，見過了，千載春秋黃粱一夢，早就盡興。", "name": "夕"}, "figure_art": "avgnew_2015_dusk_1#1$1"}, {"id": 220, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avgnew_2015_dusk_1#8$1"}}, {"id": 221, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……有你們在，我也不算孤單。", "name": "夕"}, "figure_art": "avgnew_2015_dusk_1#8$1"}, {"id": 222, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 223, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "畫家拋下筆，身形遁去。"}}, {"id": 224, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_wing"}}, {"id": 225, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "長空澄澈如白卷，有一行羽獸掠過。"}}, {"id": 226, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 227, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 228, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 229, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 230, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 231, "prop": "image", "attributes": {"image": "47_i12", "screenadapt": "coverall", "xScale": 1.1, "yScale": 1.1, "y": 30.0}}, {"id": 232, "prop": "ImageTween", "attributes": {"xScaleFrom": 1.1, "yScaleFrom": 1.1, "xScaleTo": 1.0, "yScaleTo": 1.0, "duration": 30.0, "yTo": 0.0}}, {"id": 233, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 3.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 234, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$drift_intro", "key": "$drift_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 235, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_drtywndblw"}}, {"id": 236, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 237, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_cloakmovement"}}, {"id": 238, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "長短還合身嗎？", "name": "績"}}, {"id": 239, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "布料只有這一匹，要是不小心裁壞了，我可沒地再找新的去。", "name": "績"}}, {"id": 240, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "再合適不過。", "name": "望"}}, {"id": 241, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "事到如今，再問這句話或許遲了一點……", "name": "績"}}, {"id": 242, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……勝算有幾成？", "name": "績"}}, {"id": 243, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "半目勝負，生死之間。", "name": "望"}}, {"id": 244, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "聽起來，很容易虧得血本無歸啊……也沒有退路就是了。", "name": "績"}}, {"id": 245, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "何時動手？", "name": "績"}}, {"id": 246, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "萬事俱備，只欠……", "name": "望"}}, {"id": 247, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 248, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 249, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.6, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 250, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "我很快就來見你了。", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 251, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "當你睜開眼，看到這件長袍上圖案的時候，你會回想起當時的感受嗎？", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 252, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "千年前，那深入靈魂的恐懼，刻入骨髓的恥辱。", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 253, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "你最好還記得。", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 254, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "我很快，就來見你了。", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 255, "prop": "subtitle", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 256, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 257, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 258, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 3.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 259, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 260, "prop": "image", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 261, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "35_mini01_villagevacancy", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 262, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 263, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"key": "$calm_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 264, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 265, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_140#2", "duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 266, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 267, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "黍姑娘，我們這裡的田都已經荒了幾年了，真的還能種莊稼？方法用對了，就能種出糧食？", "name": "農人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_140#2"}, {"id": 268, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_2025_shu_1#9$1"}}, {"id": 269, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "當然能。", "name": "黍"}, "figure_art": "avg_2025_shu_1#9$1"}, {"id": 270, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "每片土地適合的作物不一樣，改良土壤，還要用合適的方法。", "name": "黍"}, "figure_art": "avg_2025_shu_1#9$1"}, {"id": 271, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這撥種子已經種下去了，等秋天的時候，你們就能看到結果了。", "name": "黍"}, "figure_art": "avg_2025_shu_1#9$1"}, {"id": 272, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_140#2"}}, {"id": 273, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "黍姑娘，您從哪來？", "name": "農人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_140#2"}, {"id": 274, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "您看起來這麼年輕，對這田裡的事懂得還真多……您說您是天師府的天師？天師是什麼呢？", "name": "農人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_140#2"}, {"id": 275, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_2025_shu_1#9$1"}}, {"id": 276, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "就是專門研究知識，再教給更多人的人。", "name": "黍"}, "figure_art": "avg_2025_shu_1#9$1"}, {"id": 277, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_140#2"}}, {"id": 278, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "真了不起啊……", "name": "農人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_140#2"}, {"id": 279, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "黍姑娘，您先忙著，我去幫您倒杯水去。", "name": "農人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_140#2"}, {"id": 280, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 281, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_walk_n"}}, {"id": 282, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 283, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.5}}, {"id": 284, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "七月亨葵，九月授衣。春日載陽，有鳴倉庚……", "name": "稚嫩的童聲"}}, {"id": 285, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "九月築場圃，十月納禾農，黍稷重穋，禾麻菽麥……", "name": "稚嫩的童聲"}}, {"id": 286, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_2025_shu_1#3$1"}}, {"id": 287, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "黍"}, "figure_art": "avg_2025_shu_1#3$1"}, {"id": 288, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 289, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 290, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 291, "prop": "curtain", "attributes": {"direction": 0.0, "fillfrom": 0.01, "fillto": 0.1, "block": "false"}}, {"id": 292, "prop": "curtain", "attributes": {"direction": 4.0, "fillfrom": 0.01, "fillto": 0.1, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 293, "prop": "image", "attributes": {"image": "47_i13_1", "screenadapt": "coverall", "xScale": 1.1, "yScale": 1.1}}, {"id": 294, "prop": "ImageTween", "attributes": {"xTo": 40.0, "duration": 50.0}}, {"id": 295, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 296, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 297, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "“七月亨葵，九月授衣。”", "name": "績"}}, {"id": 298, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "大荒城冬天來得早，今年也得早點準備冬衣。", "name": "績"}}, {"id": 299, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "姐姐，要不要幫你做一套新衣裳？", "name": "績"}}, {"id": 300, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我哪裡用得上……", "name": "黍"}}, {"id": 301, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我新琢磨了一種紡織辦法，織出來的緞面又輕又耐用，顏色也好看。", "name": "績"}}, {"id": 302, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我都想好了新衣裳的樣子，你穿上肯定好看。", "name": "績"}}, {"id": 303, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "哎，隨你吧……", "name": "黍"}}, {"id": 304, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "姐姐……", "name": "績"}}, {"id": 305, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這樣算是“人”的生活嗎？", "name": "績"}}, {"id": 306, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "好像……也算快樂。", "name": "績"}}, {"id": 307, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 308, "prop": "curtain", "attributes": {"direction": 0.0, "fillfrom": 0.1, "fillto": 0.0, "block": "false", "fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 309, "prop": "curtain", "attributes": {"direction": 4.0, "fillfrom": 0.1, "fillto": 0.0, "block": "false", "fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 310, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 311, "prop": "image", "attributes": {"image": "47_i13_2", "screenadapt": "coverall", "xScale": 1.0, "yScale": 1.0, "fadetime": 0.0}}, {"id": 312, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_reedmarshes", "volume": 0.0, "loop": "true", "channel": "a"}}, {"id": 313, "prop": "SoundVolume", "attributes": {"volume": 0.7, "fadetime": 2.0, "channel": "a"}}, {"id": 314, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 315, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 316, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "是啊。", "name": "黍"}}, {"id": 317, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你已經真實地活過。"}}, {"id": 318, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 319, "prop": "StopSound", "attributes": {"channel": "a", "fadetime": 3.0}}, {"id": 320, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 3.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 321, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 322, "prop": "image", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 323, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "bg_outcounty", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 324, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 325, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 326, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1236_1#9$1", "duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 327, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 328, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "先生，您教我那些行商的道理，我都已經了然於心。只是最後，我還是有一件事不解。", "name": "績"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1236_1#9$1"}, {"id": 329, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "世間萬物，飄渺如幻，我到底該如何估價？", "name": "績"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1236_1#9$1"}, {"id": 330, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "focus": "n"}}, {"id": 331, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "哈哈……", "name": "年邁的商人"}}, {"id": 332, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你看，我身上這個玉墜值幾文錢？", "name": "年邁的商人"}}, {"id": 333, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1236_1#9$1"}}, {"id": 334, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我知道這枚玉墜，不過是個尋常物件，在地攤上，最多賣二兩銀子。", "name": "績"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1236_1#9$1"}, {"id": 335, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "focus": "n"}}, {"id": 336, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "可是這玉墜是我娘留給我的遺物，我從記事起就一直帶著。對我來說，它價值無量。", "name": "年邁的商人"}}, {"id": 337, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "估價，到頭來，估的還是人心。", "name": "年邁的商人"}}, {"id": 338, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1236_1#3$1"}}, {"id": 339, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……我記著了。", "name": "績"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1236_1#3$1"}, {"id": 340, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "focus": "n"}}, {"id": 341, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "快入夏了……江南荔枝正是好時候。", "name": "年邁的商人"}}, {"id": 342, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "北部天乾，種出來的荔枝就是不甜，比不上故鄉的味道。", "name": "年邁的商人"}}, {"id": 343, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "本想這次回到老家，能再開一條商路，把南方的荔枝賣到北方去，結果隔著一道江，再也回不去了。", "name": "年邁的商人"}}, {"id": 344, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1236_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 345, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "可恨這一場雨，實在不是時候。", "name": "績"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1236_1#1$1"}, {"id": 346, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1236_1#9$1"}}, {"id": 347, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "等過兩天入夏了，也等您身子暖起來，我們就僱條船過江。", "name": "績"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1236_1#9$1"}, {"id": 348, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "focus": "n"}}, {"id": 349, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "算了……我心裡清楚，我的路，就到這了。", "name": "年邁的商人"}}, {"id": 350, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "人吶，為什麼總是要逆天而行呢……", "name": "年邁的商人"}}, {"id": 351, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……你今年，多大了？", "name": "年邁的商人"}}, {"id": 352, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1236_1#9$1"}}, {"id": 353, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我們這種人的年齡，不太好算。", "name": "績"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1236_1#9$1"}, {"id": 354, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "一定要算的話，過了小暑，剛好五十。", "name": "績"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1236_1#9$1"}, {"id": 355, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "focus": "n"}}, {"id": 356, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "看得出來，你和常人不太一樣……羨慕你有這麼長的壽命，但是轉念一想，這麼長的一生啊，得多辛苦啊……", "name": "年邁的商人"}}, {"id": 357, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不管你是什麼樣，我今年八十三了，你跟著我這麼久，認你當養子，你也不算吃虧。", "name": "年邁的商人"}}, {"id": 358, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1236_1#9$1"}}, {"id": 359, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "與您相逢一場，見過這片大地上無限風光，實屬幸事。", "name": "績"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1236_1#9$1"}, {"id": 360, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "focus": "n"}}, {"id": 361, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "相逢有緣，我也沒什麼好贈與你的。除了那點不值錢的家業，就剩這句話了。", "name": "年邁的商人"}}, {"id": 362, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1236_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 363, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "天下熙熙，皆為利來；天下攘攘，皆為利往。", "name": "績"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1236_1#2$1"}, {"id": 364, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "focus": "n"}}, {"id": 365, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……這句話，我從學做生意的第一天起，就一直念到現在。我也靠著這句話，贏了不少敵人對手。", "name": "年邁的商人"}}, {"id": 366, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "可這天下，若是一個“利”字就說盡了，那未免也太無聊了。", "name": "年邁的商人"}}, {"id": 367, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我的時間不多了，走不了多少路。若你真的有那麼漫長的壽命，那就替我去看看吧。", "name": "年邁的商人"}}, {"id": 368, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "走遍這片大地，去看看這世上是否有一個能讓普天下人共贏的“大利”。", "name": "年邁的商人"}}, {"id": 369, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "要是真的能找到的話……", "name": "年邁的商人"}}, {"id": 370, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 371, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1236_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 372, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 373, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我會記得……", "name": "績"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1236_1#1$1"}, {"id": 374, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我會去看看的。", "name": "績"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1236_1#1$1"}, {"id": 375, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 376, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 377, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 3.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 378, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 379, "prop": "Image", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 380, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 381, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": ""}}], "OPTIONTRACE": true}